All Implemented Interfaces:
com.google.common.base.Function<String,FileData>, Identifiable
public final class FileBundleData
extends AbstractFileData
implements com.google.common.base.Function<String,FileData>

Object that represents the data of a server stored file bundle. Files are used to store binary objects used during configuration. Leading prefixes "./" and "/" are removed while building the collection and ignored when querying it.
